I’ve identified one unreported edge that may materially strengthen the theft case in `GatewayTransferNative`: `withdrawToNativeChain` treats the ETH sentinel as a valid input token, but never verifies `msg.value` or wraps funds. If `zrc20 == _ETH_ADDRESS_`, the function can proceed using only resident balances.
